    <!-- xml:id="user_mgt_workflow"-->
    <title><?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20161114T105833+0100" comment="Confirm workflow with SME."?>Workflow<?oxy_comment_end?></title>
    <orderedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para>Define the positions you need for your project and identify which tasks the
                different positions will perform.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Create roughly one user role for each position.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Create users.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Assign user roles to the users.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Assign the users to organisation units.(?)</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Assign data sets to the user role(??)</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>(Optional) Group users in user groups.</para>
        </listitem>
    </orderedlist>
    <tip>
        <para>For users to be able to enter data, you must
            <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20161114T111602+0100" comment="Or assign to?"?>add<?oxy_comment_end?>
            them to both a data set and an organisational unit
            <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20161110T141614+0100" comment="Organisation unit or organisation unit level?"?>level<?oxy_comment_end?>.</para>
    </tip>
